metadata.name: Epitelio_03
metadata.description:
This piece belongs to Epitelio,  
a photo/register from a performance from in situ series_2022.

Layers that cover my body, hollow organs and mucous glands.  
Layers that will protect me from the outside, from foreign substances, from strangers, perhaps.  
Multiple layers that tighten my hair, my muscles.  
Layers that generate liquids to excrete.  
Layers that exhaust me and are difficult to wrap, to carry, to keep.

Created by Suayma Martinez Parra_2022
